Style Dockx !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky
Style eww-workspaces !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, StaysOnTop, NoHandles, EWMHIgnoreStrutHints, EWMHPlacementIgnoreWorkingArea, WindowListSkip, ClickToFocus
Style tint2 !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, StaysOnTop, NoHandles, EWMHIgnoreStrutHints, EWMHPlacementIgnoreWorkingArea, WindowListSkip, PositionPlacement 0 -0, ClickToFocus
Style eww-notifications !Title, !Borders, !Handles, StaysOnTop
