Style eww-calendar !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, StaysOnTop, NoHandles, EWMHIgnoreStrutHints, EWMHPlacementIgnoreWorkingArea, WindowListSkip, ClickToFocus
Style Fig_desktop !Title, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, StaysOnTop, NoHandles, EWMHIgnoreStrutHints, EWMHPlacementIgnoreWorkingArea, WindowListSkip, PositionPlacement 0 -0, ClickToFocus

