# Colorsets can be used to configure the color of the various
# parts of fvwm such as window decor, menus, modules, etc.
#
# Colorset Convention
#
#   0 - Default
#   1 - Inactive Windows
#   2 - Active Window
#   3 - Inactive Windows Borders
#   4 - Active Windows Borders
#   5 - Menu - Inactive Item
#   6 - Menu - Active Item
#   7 - Menu - Grayed Item
#   8 - Menu - Title
#   9 - Reserved
#  10+ Modules
#      10 - Module Default
#      11 - Module Hilight
#      12 - Module ActiveButton (Mouse Hover)
#      13 - FvwmPager Active Page
#      14 - FvwmIconMan Iconified Button

Colorset 0  fg #b6beca, bg #171B20, hi, sh, Plain, NoShape
Colorset 1  fgTint #171B20 100, bgTint #171B20 100, RootTransparent
