# Contexts:
#     R = Root Window                 rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#     W = Application Window          rIrrrr<---------^rrrrr
#     F = Frame Corners               rrrrrr[13TTTT642]rrrrr
#     S = Frame Sides                 rIrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     T = Title Bar                   rrrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     I = Icon                        rIrrrrv_________>rrrrr
#                                     rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#
#     Numbers are buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#
# Modifiers: (A)ny, (C)ontrol, (S)hift, (M)eta, (N)othing
#
# Format: Key <X>  <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
#         Mouse <X> <Context> <Modifier> <Action>

# Alt-F1 or Menu to load the root menu and Alt-Tab for a WindowList.
# Ctrl-F1/F2/F3/F4 will switch between the Virtual Desktops.
# Super_R (windows key) will launch a terminal.
#
# Open menus using other ways:
Key F1 A M Menu JGMenu
Key Menu A A Menu JGMenu

# Jump between desktops
Key 1 A 4 GotoDesk 0 0
Key 2 A 4 GotoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A 4 GotoDesk 0 2
Key 4 A 4 GotoDesk 0 3

# Execute a terminal
Key Return A 4 Exec exec kitty

# Close a running application
Key F4 A M Close

# Lock
Key l A C Exec bash ~/.scripts/lock

# Maximize a window B)
Key t WT 4 Maximize

# Generic Alt+Tab switcher
Key tab A 1 Switcher

# Window Buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#   1 - Open the WindowOps menu.
#   2 - Close on single click, Destory on double click.
#   4 - Maximize (right/middle button will only maximize vertical/horizontal)
#   6 - Iconify (minimize)
Mouse 1 1 A Menu MenuWindowOps Delete
Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize
Mouse 1 6 A Iconify

#   TitleBar: Click to Raise, Move, Double Click to Maximize
#             Mouse Wheel Up/Down to WindowShade On/Off
#   Borders: Click to  Resize
Mouse 4	T    A WindowShade True
Mouse 5	T    A Wraise, Move to Resize

# Music control
Key XF86AudioNext A A Exec playerctl next
Key XF86AudioPrev A A Exec playerctl previous
Key XF86AudioPlay A A Exec playerctl play-pause
Key XF86AudioPause A A Exec playerctl play-pause

# Brightness control
Key XF86MonBrightnessUp A A Exec bash ~/.scripts/backlight.sh inc 10
Key XF86MonBrightnessDown A A Exec bash ~/.scripts/backlight.sh dec 10

# Volume control
Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A A Exec ~/.scripts/volume.sh inc 10
Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A A Exec ~/.scripts/volume.sh dec 10
Key XF86AudioMute A A Exec ~/.scripts/volume.sh mute

# Open Rofi
# Key space A 4 Exec exec rofi -show drun

# Super + Shift + 1-4 to send to another workspace
Key 1 A 4S MovetoPage 0 0
Key 2 A 4S MovetoPage 1 0
Key 3 A 4S MovetoPage 2 0
Key 4 A 4S MovetoPage 3 0

# Screenshot
Key Print A A Exec bash $HOME/.scripts/shot.sh

# Open File Manager
Key f A 4 Exec exec thunar

# Open Browser
Key b A 4 Exec exec firefox

#   Root Window: Left Click - Main Menu
#                Right Click - WindowOps Menu
#                Middle Click - Window List Menu
#   Right click TitleBar/Borders for WindowOps Menu
Mouse 1	T    A RaiseMoveX Move Maximize
Mouse 1	FS   A RaiseMoveindowShade False
Mouse 3	R    A JGMenu
Mouse 2	R    A JGMenu
Mouse 1	R    A JGMenu
Mouse 1	I    A RaiseMoveX Move "Iconify off"
Mouse 3	T    A Menu MenuWindowOps
Mouse 3 I    A Menu MenuIconOps
Mouse 1 W HM drag-n-move
Mouse 3 W HM drag-n-resize
Mouse 2 W HM RaiseLower

# Window snapping
Key Left A 4 SnapLeft
Key Right A 4 SnapRight
Key Up A 4 SnapHalf
Key Down A 4 SnapQuarter
Key n A 4 SnapTiny

## On minimized windows
Mouse 1 I A Iconify off
Mouse 3 I A Menu MenuIconOps

